.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/10090121/Vision-Metron-TFW-Disc-lightweight-carbon-TT-wheel_Valcar-Travel-Service-team-with-disc-brakes-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/10090121/Vision-Metron-TFW-Disc-lightweight-carbon-TT-wheel_Valcar-Travel-Service-team-with-disc-brakes-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/10090121/Vision-Metron-TFW-Disc-lightweight-carbon-TT-wheel_Valcar-Travel-Service-team-with-disc-brakes-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252790\">c. <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/valcar_ts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Valcar-Travel Service</a>, photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/twilcha/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Twila Muzzi</a></figcaption></figure><p>FSA/Vision also sponsors another equally-pink pro team racing on Cannondales, the <a href=\"https://www.valcar-travelandservice.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Valcar-Travel Service</a> women’s team who ride the even harder to come by <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/05/04/giro101-tech-prototype-cannondale-aero-disc-road-bike-spotted-under-drapac/\">SuperSlice Disc</a> time trial bikes. So of course there’s a disc-brake version too. All of the tech details are the same, plus the addition of a rotor mount, hub spacing, and thru-axle compatibility. Weight claim for the Vision Metron TFW Disc DB TT wheel is even the same at 969g.</p><p>There will even be rim-brake and disc-brake tubular versions that share the same aero-optimized shape and lightweight carbon construction for traditionalist hold-outs.</p><h3>Vision Metron TFW Disc TT wheel – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3><figure id=\"attachment_252789\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252789\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/10090106/Vision-Metron-TFW-Disc-lightweight-carbon-TT-wheel_